{"tid":766803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【14億青山走犯】支那大媽抖音拍片斥日本正妹店員「為什麼不會說中國話？」","createTime":"2018-08-04T02:34:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T03:36:23.000Z","uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"913c5e6a81d6fca5d7d7071ef91a836636ecd2f6","tid":766803,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T02:34:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2508497\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2508497&d=OyPra5W0UsMmW4Xh8JxRCDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=4c62bc17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2508497&h=f8a02197\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2508497</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h0-gGSytfIw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dh0-gGSytfIw&d=OyPra5W0UsMmW4Xh8JxRCDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=c2a050ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h0-gGSytfIw</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕1名中國東北大媽前往日本觀光旅遊，竟異想天開想測試日本人會不會說中文，因此故意前往當地超商和正妹女店員討「飲料」，還斥責對方「中國話為什麼不會？」，影片上傳後引起各國網友撻伐。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpySiDaX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpySiDaX.jpg&h=b883062e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國微博8月1日上的1段影片中，顯示1名大媽拿著手機開啟錄影模式，並說「來問一下日本店裡面的小妹妹」，接著鏡頭直接對著笑臉迎人的正妹店員，向對方說「飲料」，店員眉頭一皺，發現大媽口說中文，以日文答覆「不好意思，我不知道」，不料大媽竟嘴她「中國話為什麼不會？」。<br />\n<br />\n許多華語系國家的網友看完影片後，都感到相當憤怒，紛紛留言指出「病得很嚴重啊，這就叫傻逼」、「傻逼不知道自己在哪裡」、「低能，沒文化」、「這會讓人更討厭中國」、「虧大媽問得出口」、「你日本話為什麼不會，不會就別去日本好嗎」。<br />\n<br />\n中國網友們也對東北大媽的行為感到不能理解，相繼留言提到「雖然知道這樣說不對，但是好希望這種人立刻死掉」、「智障，就算在國內的便利店裡，你也不會跑去收銀台跟人家要飲料吧」、「神經病，而且侵犯別人肖像權了」、「有病嗎？能不丟中國人臉嗎？」、「出門腦子為什麼不帶」。"},{"pid":"7c200e3ceef20499e831661293534117f3dc94fa","tid":766803,"uid":26451,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T02:41:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6343b85bdd79f6f3f64c91e6c10e6b7f51ef9e3f","tid":766803,"uid":79563,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"7c200e3ceef20499e831661293534117f3dc94fa","tid":766803,"uid":26451,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T02:41:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T02:43:26.000Z","msg":"屠得唔夠多<br />\n<br />\n得南京一個城屠, 實在太少"},{"pid":"90c390ae8aca1258d3ec8b6fc6f0eed4c2e95aa0","tid":766803,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T02:54:36.000Z","msg":"仆街上次去日本個7仔店員主動同我講普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"297d77e30b2925e43e5c95fed5251ea364c88b53","tid":766803,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90c390ae8aca1258d3ec8b6fc6f0eed4c2e95aa0","tid":766803,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T02:54:36.000Z","msg":"仆街上次去日本個7仔店員主動同我講普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T03:12:40.000Z","msg":"留學生PT?"},{"pid":"b7c0b2be061f19c51b9a04c2d6d637875c966bf0","tid":766803,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"297d77e30b2925e43e5c95fed5251ea364c88b53","tid":766803,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90c390ae8aca1258d3ec8b6fc6f0eed4c2e95aa0","tid":766803,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T02:54:36.000Z","msg":"仆街上次去日本個7仔店員主動同我講普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T03:12:40.000Z","msg":"留學生PT?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T03:13:52.000Z","msg":"個類掛<br />\n冇深究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif